# CONCLAVE — local demo environment variables.
#
# Copy to .env (git-ignored) and fill in. Only the demo Makefile targets
# (`make demo-fraud` / `make demo-security` / `*-local`) read these.

# ───── Anthropic (default judge backend) ─────
# Required for `make demo-fraud` / `make demo-security`. NOT required for
# the `-local` variants (those use the Ollama overlay).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional model override. The spec locks Haiku 4.5 for shipped demos +
# benchmarks (rule #6); don't change for published numbers.
# JUDGE_LLM_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5-20251001

# ───── Domain (rarely overridden; the demo targets set this) ─────
# fraud | security
# SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=fraud
